/*                  triangular matrix l, diagonal matrix d, and unit */
/*                  upper triangular matrix u, and solution of linear */
/*                  system) */
/*         nnsc   (solution of linear system for additional right-hand */
/*                  side using ldu factorization from nnfc) */
